OL,3,C'Absolute gentleman', 27, died after
OL,4,Cbecoming 'trapped in machine'
OL,6,FA 27-year-old man "became trapped in a
OL,7,Fmachine" at a Cardiff recycling site
OL,8,Fand suffered fatal injuries, a inquest
OL,9,Fhas heard.
OL,11,FThe hearing into the death of Kyle
OL,12,FLlewellyn Colcomb opened on Friday at
OL,13,FPontypridd Coroners' Court
OL,15,FCoroner's officer Beverley Morgan said
OL,16,FMr Colcomb was working at Atlantic
OL,17,FRecycling in Rumney on July 8 when he
OL,18,F"became trapped in a machine, suffered
OL,19,Ffatal injuries, and died at the scene".
