OL,6,FHis death was declared at 12.52pm that
OL,7,Fday.
OL,9,FA post-mortem examination by Dr
OL,10,FRichard Jones of the University
OL,11,FHospital of Wales gave a provisional
OL,12,Fcause of death as compression asphyxia
OL,13,Fwith blunt force injuries to the lower
OL,14,Ftrunk.
OL,16,FThe court heard Mr Colcomb was born in
OL,17,FCardiff and lived in Newport.
