OL,6,FCoroner Patricia Morgan said she would
OL,7,Fopen an inquest because she had
OL,8,F"reason to suspect his death was
OL,9,Funnatural" but would suspend it to
OL,10,Fallow South Wales Police and the
OL,11,FHealth and Safety Executive to
OL,12,F"continue their investigation and any
OL,13,Fproceedings that arise as a result of
OL,14,Fthat investigation".
OL,16,FShe added: "I will direct both police
OL,17,Fand the Health and Safety Executive to
OL,18,Fmaintain contact with me so they can
OL,19,Finform me when proceedings have
OL,20,Fconcluded.
