OL,6,F"A decision will then be made as to
OL,7,Fwhether the inquest is resumed. I wish
OL,8,Fto take this opportunity to express
OL,9,Fdeep condolences to the family of Mr
OL,10,FColcomb at this tragic time."
OL,12,FSouth Wales Police said Mr Colcomb was
OL,13,Fa contractor carrying out maintenance
OL,14,Fat the site. Last week his colleagues
OL,15,Fat M&B Hydraulics paid tribute in an
OL,16,Fonline statement.
OL,18,FIt read: "We are all absolutely
OL,19,Fdevastated at the loss of Kyle, who
OL,20,Fwas an outstanding fitter, an absolute
OL,21,Fgentleman and an all-around nice guy.
